{"word":"τυφόω","slug":"τυφόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τυφόω</b></el> <el>(τῡφόω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ώσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τῦφος'><el>τῦφος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to wrap in smoke;</i> <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> in <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>τετύφωμαι</el>, <i>to be in the clouds, to be crazed, demented</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}